Storage.description:
Automatically created at `game.storage` if `game.Storage.id` is set.

    game.Storage.id = 'com.company.mygame';

    game.storage.set('highScore', 1000);
    var highScore = game.storage.get('highscore');

Timer.description:
Basic timer.

__Example__

    var timer = new game.Timer(2);
    if(timer.delta() >= 0) {
        timer.set(2);
    }
